<li class='cover' id='bookCover_6117055'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/6117055-the-greatest-show-on-earth"><img alt="The Greatest Show on Earth: The Evidence for Evolution" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1302127919l/6117055._SX98_.jpg" />
